:A double [[diminutive]] of '''[[ruka#Slovak|ruka]]''' (''[[hand]]''):
:'''[[ruka#Slovak|ruka]]''' + '''[[-ka#Slovak|-ka]]''' + '''[[-ka#Slovak|-ka]]''' = '''[[rúčka#Slovak|rúčka]]''' + '''[[-ka#Slovak|-ka]]''' = '''ručička''' (''tiny little hand'')

